  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Inghams guests have the Platinum All Inclusive Package, which includes breakfast, lunch and dinner and a larger range of dining options than the standard package.</p>
<p>There are four restaurants to choose from at the Britannia; Britannia Buffet, Lido a la carte, Lido Pizzeria and the Floating Pool Chiurasco, as well as these restaurants at <a data-udi="umb://document/607cb51dd2fd45daabd1fe4381945064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/607cb51dd2fd45daabd1fe4381945064}" title="Hotel Bazzoni">Hotel Bazzoni</a>; Bazzoni Buffet and Simply Pasta. You can eat at all of these restaurants for no additional cost but reservations are required for a la carte dining. </p>
<p>The package also includes drinks, cocktails and selected brands of spirits and liquors at the bars in both hotels. </p>
<p>If you're planning on heading out for the day you can order a packed lunch, at reception the day before (order by 7pm) and it will be ready for you the next morning. </p>
<p><strong>Britania Buffet </strong>is the main restaurant at the hotel where you can have breakfast, lunch and dinner. A continental buffet breakfast is served from 7am - 10am and hot options are available from 8am - 9.30am. There are three show cooking islands so you can watch the chefs at work, cooking up fresh tasty options like pizza and pasta for lunch and dinner. Open for lunch from 12pm - 2pm and dinner from 6.30pm - 9pm.</p>
<p><strong>Lido a la Carte</strong> is on the lake edge and offers local cuisine with pool views. You can have breakfast here with waiter service too. It's close to the hotel's beach and has its’ own bar serving all-inclusive drinks (excluding spirits) from 10am until 6pm from May to September. </p>
<p><strong>Lido Pizzeria</strong> is also on the roof terrace with amazing views. </p>
<p><strong>Floating Pool Chiurasco Restaurant </strong>is beside the hotel's floating pool. The restaurant has a seating area over the lake and serves things like fresh fish and pasta dishes. </p>
<p><strong>Floating Pool Cocktail Bar </strong>is also beside the pool. There's often live music here too (normally open May to September).</p>
<p><strong>The Main Bar</strong> is downstairs and has a large seating area. Platinum all inclusive drinks are included in the price. Open 8am - 11pm.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
