  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Britannia Excelsior has a great location just steps away from the ferry landing stage with breath taking views of the bay towards <a data-udi="umb://document/d3611d3782e0494ead59e534458bcdd6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3611d3782e0494ead59e534458bcdd6}" title="Bellagio">Bellagio</a>. We love the pool here, it's the largest floating pool in Europe! You'll get a Deluxe Room and an all-inclusive upgrade as standard, so there's plenty of choice when it comes to dining. </p>]]></listingDescription>
