  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are the upgraded rooms of the hotel. They have plenty of space and can sleep up to three people. The third bed is a single sofa bed. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, safe, fridge, hairdryer and shower. Rooms with a lake view and lake view &amp; balcony are available for a supplement.</p>
